Synopsis

A few youngsters who are active in blog and social network sites decided to organize an exclusive show in Bangalore. The main coordinator of the show is famous in the blog as 'Olipporali'. In the final rehearsal when everyone arrives, Oliporali alone has not come. All others wait for him for a long time. Then they realize that they have only meager information about the whereabouts of Oliporali. They find themselves in dilemma.
